{
  "stem": "6159.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '44 January.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Over a year, I guess.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Long time.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I really don't know it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I came back with-- no, no it wasn't a year, no, no.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Six to eight months.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Must have been more than that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Must have been more than that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I lost track of the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It felt like a long time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe it wasn't such a long time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For me, it was a very bad time because leaving these other people and-- and running all the time down in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll tell you what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My boss was sort of not a religious Jew because he was married to a non-Jew.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they kept Christmas.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my husband, I have to call him my husband because later on he was my husband, and we went to see them where they lived for a Christmas celebration.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, they invited us for dinner.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when we went there and left after dinner, I was hit by a Russian part of the bomb.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They bombed already.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were not properly in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They bombed from Buda to Pest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were on the street, about 10 o'clock at night, and we heard that-- that the bomb is coming.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was in a leather jacket, and he was sort of covering me with the jacket, and hovering above me, so I don't get the-- the part of the bomb, if it hits us.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And yet he was escaping, and I got here a very bad piece of shell.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
